  "text": "HomeCareersMega Mega Projects is a multi-label full-service brand development agency that specializes in jewelry.Mega Mega Projects Mega Mega Projects is a multi-label full-service brand development agency that specializes in jewelry. We combine public relations, sales, and digital strategy to grow brands in today’s digital world.Please do not apply if your graduation date is May or June 2025Responsibilities● Manage fashion + 14K client accounts● Track and distribute press placements● Maintain and update media lists● Assist with clipping when needed● Assist on 18K client accounts when needed● Communicate with editors regularly to foster relationships and ensure top placements● Craft relevant trend, collection, and event pitches● Help plan and execute seasonal Press Preview● Plan and manage client events \u0026 desksides when needed● Manage inventory for assigned clients● Support PR Director on high level projectsRequirements● 3+ Years of PR● MUST have account management experience● Existing editor relationships in the fashion and fine jewelry industry● Experience with Fashion GPS preferred● Exceptional communication and writing skills and experience with pitching● Attention to detail and consistent follow through● Ability to multitask, delegate, and manage● Highly self-motivated, willing to take initiative● This is a semi-hybrid role, with at least three days in office required● Some travel may be required depending on the needs of the teamCompensation: $65k-$75kTo apply for this position, please email your resume to Jessica at : jkiraly@megamegaprojects.com@megamegaprojectsScroll to ContinueRecommended ArticlesSubscribe to Our Newsletter",
