003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MTkyNjExMDQ3MzMxMzQyMDcz/mega-mega-projects-mmp-logo.png 380w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MTkyNjExMDQ3MzMxMzQyMDcz/mega-mega-projects-mmp-logo.png 620w, https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MTkyNjExMDQ3MzMxMzQyMDcz/mega-mega-projects-mmp-logo.png 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"mega mega projects mmp logo\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/t_share/MTkyNjExMDQ3MzMxMzQyMDcz/mega-mega-projects-mmp-logo.png\" data-src=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MTkyNjExMDQ3MzMxMzQyMDcz/mega-mega-projects-mmp-logo.png\" height=\"300\" width=\"1050\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMega Mega Projects\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://megamegaprojects.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eMega Mega Projects \u003c/a\u003eis a multi-label full-service brand development agency that specializes in jewelry. We combine public relations, sales, and digital strategy to grow brands in today’s digital world.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cbr/\u003ePlease do not apply if your graduation date is May or June 2025\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eResponsibilities\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e● Manage fashion + 14K client accounts\u003cbr/\u003e● Track and distribute press placements\u003cbr/\u003e● Maintain and update media lists\u003cbr/\u003e● Assist with clipping when needed\u003cbr/\u003e● Assist on 18K client accounts when needed\u003cbr/\u003e● Communicate with editors regularly to foster relationships and ensure top placements\u003cbr/\u003e● Craft relevant trend, collection, and event pitches\u003cbr/\u003e● Help plan and execute seasonal Press Preview\u003cbr/\u003e● Plan and manage client events \u0026amp; desksides when needed\u003cbr/\u003e● Manage inventory for assigned clients\u003cbr/\u003e● Support PR Director on high level projects\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eRequirements\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e● 3+ Years of PR\u003cbr/\u003e● MUST have account management experience\u003cbr/\u003e● Existing editor relationships in the fashion and fine jewelry industry\u003cbr/\u003e● Experience with Fashion GPS preferred\u003cbr/\u003e● Exceptional communication and writing skills and experience with pitching\u003cbr/\u003e● Attention to detail and consistent follow through\u003cbr/\u003e● Ability to multitask, delegate, and manage\u003cbr/\u003e● Highly self-motivated, willing to take initiative\u003cbr/\u003e● This is a semi-hybrid role, with at least three days in office required\u003cbr/\u003e● Some travel may be required depending on the needs of the team\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCompensation\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cem\u003e: $65k-$75k\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/em\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/em\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTo apply for this position, please email your resume to Jessica at : \u003c/strong\u003e\u003ca href=\"mailto:jkiraly@megamegaprojects.com\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ejkiraly@megamegaprojects.com\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/megamegaprojects/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e@megamegaprojects\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Co